metadata.name: Atrium Membership Card - Founder
metadata.description:
Proper Digital's “Atrium Membership Cards” are NFTs that bring In Real Life (“IRL”) real estate to Web3. Atrium Membership Cards will connect IRL real estate investors with Web3 investors and create a community around the digitization of real property. Atrium Membership Cardholders will have unprecedented access to real estate information, future projects, community, education, and many additional perks.

The Atrium Membership Cards have 3 tiers - Founders (Black/Black), Investor (Black/Gold), and Community (Black/Silver). Access will vary depending on level of membership. Atrium Membership Cardholders will be on the cutting-edge of Web3 and witness firsthand how IRL property becomes digital properly.
